CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 29, 1961, pg. 9 reads: "Model - Mrs. Rose Simmons of Pittsburgh, one of the models for the Beautician's Fashion Show at the Fort Pitt Hotel recently, also will model at the Alpha Kappa Alpha Conference in Indianapolis, Aug. 22-24.  She wears an advance copy of a design by Mrs. Clara Tyson. - Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing two-piece pinstriped bathing suit and high heels, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for Beauticians' Fashion Show
